name: VI - The Lovers
description:
The symbology of the tarot is quite profound, the card of lovers reveals much more than a mere love decision, it is linked to the constant struggle between reason and emotion, Cupid shows that the path of the heart will probably prevail. This card carries the dilemma of decisions, communication and duality. It is about relationship, but not just loving, it can be family, professional, affective, any kind of relationship between people.
